Step 1 : Install rosaris package 

Step 2 : Connect the robot and turn on, and then check to which serial port it is connected using command  $dmesg |grep tty 

Step 4:  Considering robot is conected to /dev/ttyUSB0, Change the permission of /dev/ttyUSB0 using command  $sudo chmod 666 /dev/ttyUSB0

Step 3 : run the rosaria package, $rosrun rosaria RosAria _port:=/dev/ttyUSB0

Note : Do not need drivers for Belkin serial to usb adapter on ubuntu
